    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>The video below includes some of our widely-used reports. Below the video are links to additional reports in RepairQ.</p><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/M-YOqviil2A\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/M-YOqviil2A</a><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1937866763/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"ReportingResources(withVideo)-CashReporting\">Cash Reporting</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934917678\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Accounting System Reporting</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934295071\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Cash Flow</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934229524\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Cash Reconciliation</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934196764\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Taxes</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1939472413\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tip Report</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ReportingResources(withVideo)-SalesReporting\">Sales Reporting</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934524447\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maintaining an Accurate Profitability Report</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934753845\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Revenue, Cost of Goods Sold (COGS), Cost of Services, and Cost of Refurbs</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933803776\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Waived Charges</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934753798\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Sales Summary and Sales Details</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934557198\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Wage Expense</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934393345\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Check Your Gross Profit Margins by Item Type</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934360593\" rel=\"nofollow\">Real-Time Profitability Report</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ReportingResources(withVideo)-CustomerReporting\">Customer Reporting</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933803749\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Marketing List</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936326807\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Customer Referrals</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936654444\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Customer Segments</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ReportingResources(withVideo)-InventoryReporting\">Inventory Reporting</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934721039\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Usage</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934721025\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Orders</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934327847\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Expense</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1932427609\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Shrinkage</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934557185\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Valuation</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934196750\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory Valuation Snapshot</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934589953\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Inventory End of Year (EOY) Snapshot Archive</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"ReportingResources(withVideo)-ProductivityReporting\">Productivity Reporting</h3><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933377814\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Repairs by Device</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933803762\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Repairs by Technician</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933246837\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Accounting Journal Entries</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934327922\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Receivables and Invoice Aging</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1939570735\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Repairs by Technician and Item</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934524434\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Pending Revenue and Tickets Unpaid</a></p></li></ul><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1934196737\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Returned Repairs by Tech</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
